<emphasis box="[140,316,2088,2121]" pageId="4" pageNumber="10">Distribution.</emphasis>
Widely distributed across the 
<collectingCountry box="[743,903,2088,2121]" name="Philippines" pageId="4" pageNumber="10">Philippines</collectingCountry>
